{"id": 2833, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些公司福利，会让你有“拿到手才发现都是套路”的感觉？", "description": "来说说除了周末团建、弹性工作制、股票期权之外，你还见过哪些“看起来很美”的福利？（题图来自：iStock ️©️ CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 10345, "comment_count": 23, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190311122510Y8xBInmTtQg6DOAd.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-17T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5505, "title": "哪些公司福利，会让你有“拿到手才发现都是套路”的感觉？", "content": "哪些公司福利让，会你有“拿到手才发现都是套路”的感觉？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 332459, "content": "年假到期清零，不用就作废了", "image": "img/option/option/20190312001716C9umqGX30h5eTpYD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332461, "content": "加班后可以调休，但要先得到老板批准", "image": "img/option/option/20190312001704NgBGCTFzyVSdfma1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332452, "content": "（符合一堆条件才能拿的）加班工资/租房补贴/餐补", "image": "img/option/option/20190312001915P4mBJo9FcsTRQ25r.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332458, "content": "“跟公司大佬吃饭”之类（转卖不出去）的年会特等奖", "image": "img/option/option/20190312001744j4CLW7PJaxIqX9Zd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332450, "content": "晚上九点之后才有的加班餐、加班车费", "image": "img/option/option/20190312001943qgvinhXFukPoGMV8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332454, "content": "差旅费可以报销，但只能报其中一部分", "image": "img/option/option/20190312001901RMnulK8WoFiOtIhv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332451, "content": "零食、肥宅快乐水无限量供应", "image": "img/option/option/20190312001928PzewOMloj4UAybDH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332449, "content": "电商公司员工的“专享内部价格”", "image": "img/option/option/20190312002125JsvkOKrImz0eGHSF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332462, "content": "还行吧，这些对我还是蛮有用的", "image": "img/option/option/20190312001651nF4waJdmLN3srvPk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}